<footer class="footer bg-base-100 pl-14 pr-8 py-8 shadow print:hidden">
  <div class="container mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row">
    <div class="w-2/3">
      <h3 class="footer-title">About</h3>
      <p>
        Eli Gundry is a full stack web developer that loves JavaScript, devops and web standards. When he isn't coding,
        he's {% emojiText "👨‍🍳", "chef emoji cause I'm cooking", "cooking up something mean in the kitchen" %},
        {% emojiText "🎾", "tennis ball", "playing tennis" %} or {% emojiText "🐈‍⬛🐈", "my cats!", "annoying his cats" %}.
        He is also a <a href="/web0.html">{% emojiText "✳️", "feel the html.energy", "web0 evangelist" %}</a> and thinks
        everyone can benefit from writing some HTML.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="w-1/3">
      <h3 class="footer-title">Social</h3>
      <div>
        {% for link in social %}
          <a href="{{ link.href }}" class="btn btn-sm btn-square btn-primary" title="{{ link.label }}">
            <i class="{{ link.icon }} text-2xl"></i>
          </a>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
